collections.name: CorgiKings
collections.description:
CorgiKings is an exclusive NFT collection celebrating the royalty, charm, and legacy of the Corgi Kingdom. Each NFT features a unique, hand-crafted Corgi King or legendary character, ruling over the vast lands of the Canine Clans.

Inspired by medieval fantasy and noble heritage, these Corgis are more than just collectibles—they are symbols of leadership, loyalty, and strength. From the mighty King Barkington I to the fearsome Baron Von Poodle, each character plays a crucial role in the Corgi Kingdom’s epic tale.

collections.name: Seckinger's Faded Ghosts
collections.description: Drifting between worlds, Faded Ghosts are spectral beings whispering from beyond. No two ghosts are the same—every one is a rare manifestation of color, glow, and form. You might find one hiding in the clouds, emerging from the sea, or glimmering in the sunset. Owners will continue to discover unique things about each one.

collections.name: ELUSIVE SHADOWS
collections.description: She is a phantom in the night, a legend woven through time. From the most secure museums to the most guarded vaults, her hands reclaim relics thought to be lost forever. But she never disappears without a mark—every heist leaves behind a riddle, a hidden clue for those daring enough to chase her trail. Can you unravel the mystery, predict her next move, and discover the artifact she’ll steal next? Step into the game, own a piece of this enigma, and join the hunt. Elusiva is a collection of 1248 unique NFTs, blending mystery, adventure, and the allure of the unknown. Each piece is a fusion of AI-generated art and storytelling, inviting collectors to decode her next great heist

collections.name: Avatars 1948
collections.description:
The primary objective of this project was to create new truly modernist generative portraits in the style of the modernist artist (named Gobardhan Ash) who had made 'Avatar' like works in the late 1940's and decades ahead of the Avatar/PFP NFT craze. We believe that digital art's purpose is to showcase serious modernist works. Inspired by a project dating back to 1948, we embarked on this venture with great enthusiasm and are thrilled with the outcomes. This is Modernism, this is Fine Art !

The images are very high resolution ~10MB each and can therefore be printed out on canvas, matted paper, metal, glass, etc. and framed for display. 

The works are copyrighted VAu 1-511-229 at the United States Register of Copyrights.

collections.name: Orsi The Red ones
collections.description:
Orsi The Red ones 

Orsi The Red Ones is a visionary NFT project that merges surreal elegance with digital artistry, capturing the ethereal beauty of majestic horses in a dreamlike dance. Each piece in this collection embodies grace and nobility, with fluid, elongated forms and intricate filigree-like manes that flow like liquid fire.

At the heart of Orsi The Red Ones is the symbolism of connection—two horses standing in harmony, their heads touching, legs crossed in an artistic stance that evokes strength, unity, and transcendence. The striking contrast of fire-red ink strokes against fine detailing creates a sense of movement and depth, bringing each artwork to life.

Blending classical inspiration with modern digital techniques, Orsi The Red ones, is a tribute to timeless beauty, refined power, and the boundless imagination of the digital age.

collections.name: Confrontation – The Inner Battle
collections.description:
This artwork symbolizes the deep, inner war with my demons – those shadows that have controlled me for years, steering my thoughts and actions. I allowed them to guide me, to hold me back, to hide my true self. But this battle has taken a new direction.

What once had control over me is losing its power the moment I make it visible. These demons are a part of me, but I now acknowledge them without letting them define me. They exist, but they no longer hold me captive.

By expressing them through images, by giving them space and exposing them, I transform their energy. They are no longer my burden – they become my strength. This confrontation is not a surrender; it is a liberation.

This artwork is a testament to my journey back to myself. A symbol of self-determination, acceptance, and the courage to face one’s inner shadows. Because only when we dare to look our fears in the eye do they lose their power.

1000 unique collectible characters with proof of ownership stored on the Ethereum blockchain.

CryptoApePunks are one of the earliest and most iconic

and were the inspiration for the ERC-721 standard
